cnder und bis 1981 Leiter des Centre for the Study of Communication and Culture in London. 1981-87 Provinzial der Schweizer Provinz. 1988-89 Superior der Jesuitenkommunit\u00e4t in Sch\u00f6nbrunn."]], "wiki_links": [{"item": "http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q78057161", "itemLabel": "Stefan Bamberger", "dhsid": "044584", "namefr": "", "articlefr": "", "namede": "", "articlede": "", "nameit": "", "articleit": "", "nameen": "", "articleen": "", "instanceof": "http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q5", "instanceofLabel": "\u00eatre humain", "gndid": "13385907X"}], "wikidata_url": "http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q78057161", "wikipedia_page_title": null, "added_wikidata_wikipedia_to_text_links": true, "_initial": null, "url": "https://hls-dhs-dss.ch/de/articles/044584/2016-11-25"}